**Idea:**
using two pointer left and right
there are **4 Possible Cases** that left and right are Pointing to : 
1.  **L  and. L** (all in between dominos will fall on left side) So mark all dominos to L from left to right 
2. **L and R** (left pointer will fall to left and right to right so dominos in between will be as they were before) 
3.  **R and L** (from left side dominos will start falling to right and from right side dominos will fall down to left )
4.  **R and R** (all in b/w dominos will fall in right side) So mark all dominos to R from left to right

