but we still have two case here.
case 1 Either left or right is 0
		so, if left[i] + right[i] < 0 is left, > 0 is right
case 2 Neither left nor right is 0
		in this case, if left[i] + right[i] < 0 means close to right beacse we start from 1 and we have 2 3 4 5 6 the smaller the number, the closer the distance. so it is R
