**Explantion :**

we can create Lenght N strings from Length N-1 string by applying the defined rules to it.

Strings that have ended in "a" can only create strings with "e" ending.
Strings that have ended in "e" can create strings ending with "a"  or "i"
.....


This way we can say that at next step how many strings we would have that ends in each vowel.
We keep a track of endings at each step and go to the next step till we find the desired length.


