# **KeyPoint : We are making the string backwards.**
**Suppose we want to make a string of size k;
then 'a' can be added at with all the string of size (k-1) starting with 'e';
similarly 'e' with all string of size (k-1) starting with 'a' and 'i';
similarly 'i' with 'a','e','o','u';
and 'o' with 'i' & 'u'
