Memo[c, i] saved total number of vowel permutation which starts with character c and has a length of i+1.
"$" serves as the root of the vowels graph.
```
def countVowelPermutation(n):
	graph = {
		"$":"aeiou",
		"a":"e",
		"e":"ai",
		"i":"aeou",
		"o":"iu",
		"u":"a",
	}
	memo = {(c,0):1 for c in "aeiou"}
	M = 10**9+7
	def dfs(x, n):
		if (x,n) not in memo
			memo[x,n] = sum(dfs(y, n-1) for y in graph[x]) % M
		return memo[x,n]
	return dfs("$", n)
```

